                    "text": "Mwana wenyu akura kusvika pahurefu hunodarika zvakajairika pazera nerudzi rwake. Kazhinji izvi harisi dambudziko uye zvinogona kuva mucherechedzo wemaumbirwo (genetics) ake, asi munogona kutaura nezvazvo nemushandi wezvehutano kuchipatara chirir pedo nemi. Rambai muchitevedzera kurudziro dzamakapiwa nekuongorora kukura kwemwana wenyu nguva nenguva."
