                    "text": "Wenze kuhle! Umntanakho ukhula kuhle ngobude okuhambelana kumbe okuphezulu kancane kulalokho okukhangelelweyo eminyakeni yokuzalwa lebulilini bakhe. Qhubeka ulandela okukhuthazwayo kwezokudla kuhle, imisebenzi kumbe imidlalo eqinisa umzimba lokulala, njalo unanzelele ukukhula komntwana."
