                    "text": "Umntwana sekhule waba mude ukwedlula lokho okukhangelelweyo eminyakeni yokuzalwa lasebulilini bakhe. Lokhu akwandanga ukuba luhlupho njalo kungabe kubangelwa lufuzo kodwa lanxa kunjalo xoxisana labezempilakahle ngakho. Qhubeka ulandela okukhuthazwayo osuqalile ukukwenza njalo ulandelele ukukhula komntwana ngezigaba ezihleliweyo.&nbsp;"
